Effective Date: August 5, 2025

1. What Information We Collect
B.R.O.K.E. collects and stores the following information to provide its features:

    Your Discord User ID

    Messages sent to the Bot (such as commands and macros)

    Dice roll results and macros

2. How We Use Your Information
We use this information to:

    Enable dice rolling and macro features

    Store and display your roll history

    Provide secret/private roll functionality

3. Data Sharing
Your information is never shared with third parties.
Data is only used to provide the Bot’s features to you and your server.

4. Data Security
We make reasonable efforts to protect your data, but no method of digital storage is 100% secure.
Roll histories and macros are stored as necessary for bot operation.

5. Data Retention and Removal
Data such as roll history and macros is retained as long as B.R.O.K.E. is active in your server.
If you remove the Bot from your server, your data may be deleted as part of regular maintenance.

6. Children’s Privacy
B.R.O.K.E. is not intended for users under 13.
If you believe a user under 13 is using the Bot, please report it to Discord.

7. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy at any time. Continued use of the Bot after any changes indicates your acceptance of those changes.

8. Contact
For questions or requests related to your data, contact StrixBit Studios through Discord.
